title: OO Defrag Professional v18.0.39 x86/x64.Incl.Key
description:
Unleash the hidden performance of your computer with the minimum effort. O&O Defrag Professional Edition packs file fragments quickly and securely back together to optimize your hard disk under Windows. Its functionality ranges from a fully automated defragmentation to an individual professional set up. It can do everything a truly good defragmentation software should be able to do. The new background monitoring function helps to prevent fragmentation at source. Newly added and modified files are analyzed and defragmented whenever they are not being accessed. O&O Defrag makes sure that your hard disk is constantly performing at its peak.

Highlights
 New Use over a Smartphone and Tablet 
 Unique Time View to see which defragmentation activity results in 
              which successful optimization
 Improved Easy-to-Use: Ideal for Beginners and Professionals
 Improved Even faster system and program starts
 Improved Defragmentation time reduced by up to 40%
 Improved Defragmentation of locked files
 Improved TRIM for SSDs of any make
 Lifetime Performance Statistics 
 Automatic deletion of free space for more privacy
 Optimizing systems with Thin Provisioning

Supports Vista, Windows 7, 8, 8.1.

Support for Windows XP has ended as of this version.

Please read Installation file for further instructions,

Enjoy!
